Have you ever explored a deserted building in Bangkok ?

   Sathorn Unique Tower, facing Chao Phraya River, is an abandoned, incomplete 49-storey tower built during 1990s. 
With its location, many photographers and urbexes pay a visit to this tower in order to find a good spot to shoot chic photos
while risking their lives of getting injured by incomplete structure inside the building.

